            "date": "2012-01-04 18:34:12", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "In bug 715337, the proposal for Firefox-3.6.x support is to move a minimal set of hardware to mtv1 for Firefox-3.6.x support.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Please specify what that would entail, with quantities of machines.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I think this will include:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "bm-xserve* (the few running 10.5)\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "moz2-darwin9-*\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "talos-rev2-tiger*\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "0.7.10 master for the rev2-tiger systems\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "buildmaster\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I'm looking for:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "* quantities\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "* anything I missed\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "* portions of geriatric that are still required (name them all - I'll sort out what's in sjc1)\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Don't worry about spares - we can find a place to stash all of the available machines without power or network, to be swapped in as necessary. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " And this isn't a commitment-in-writing -- I need this for capacity planning, and if we need to make adjustments later that's fine.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Thanks!\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "Dustin J. Mitchell [:dustin]", 
            "email": "Dustin J. Mitchell [:dustin]"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2012-01-17 09:14:56", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Honestly, once 3.6 is officially EOLed (Apr 24th), I'm fine with setting these aside in mtv and not even turning them on, beyond perhaps doing it once to make sure we can. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "In the interim, if we're going to do a final substantive release for 3.6 after this long, I suspect it would be shortly after Firefox 10 (scheduled for release on Jan 31) to try to either update 3.6 users to 10 or get them onto the new ESR. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "In rare cases we need to make code changes for this, but more often we just use snippets and increasingly-scary update notices.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "Chris Cooper [:coop]", 
            "email": "Chris Cooper [:coop]"
