                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I would very much rather not keep that hardware once it's not needed. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " At any rate, this bug is about contingency planning for a failure to EOL in time.\n", 
